author: arfrever
msg: * build/transform_libtool_scripts.sh: Fix a typo in values of some variables.

author: arfrever
msg: * build/transform_libtool_scripts.sh: auth-test dynamically loads
libsvn_auth_gnome_keyring and libsvn_auth_kwallet libraries, so preload
these libraries in auth-test.
Define LD_PRELOAD at the beginning of libtool wrapper scripts to avoid
potential problems with libtool wrapper scripts generated by future versions
of libtool.

author: gstein
msg: Tweak how we fetch an entry, and make sure that we got the real entry (not
a stub from the parent directory).
* subversion/libsvn_wc/adm_crawler.c:
(report_revisions_and_depths): use DIR_ACCESS for fetching the entry.
that's the location we want. then assert we got the desired info.

author: gstein
msg: Shift around some code in temp_get_format() yet again. wc-ng is very
aggressive about filling in PDH values and their wcroots. Any entrypoint
might update a PDH, so look for problems sooner rather than later, and
force a re-examination of the disk.
* subversion/libsvn_wc/wc_db.c:
(svn_wc__db_temp_get_format): rejigger the timing of wcroot checks.
